    "en": {
      "title": "A person who attacked Kokila's and Sohoyura's houses was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police say that a suspect was arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department yesterday (17) in connection with the incident of attacking and destroying the houses and vehicles of MP Kokila Harshani Gunawardena and her brother at Loluwagoda in Nalla police domain.",
        "The police say that these houses were also attacked and damaged during the unrest that took place after the attack on the Gallumuwadora protesters on May 9.",
        "He is scheduled to appear before the Attanagalla Magistrate's Court today (18)."
      ],
